title: Vaulted ceilings, Professional onsite management, Elevator access
posting_body: ['Just 16 miles north of Seattle, located in the picturesque city of Lynnwood, Washington, Tivalli Apartments is the embodiment of sophistication and convenience.', 'Nestled along the North Puget Sound, our community of studio, one, two and three bedroom apartment homes is meticulously outfitted with high-end contemporary finishes, sleek fixtures, and smart home technology that personify luxury and innovation.', 'Each detail is carefully considered with you in mind, including the polished granite countertops, stainless steel EnergyStar appliances, in-unit washer and dryer, and large private balconies.', '-Professional onsite management', '-Sports courts and onsite playground', '-Controlled-entry access', '-Pet friendly (breed restrictions apply)', '-App-controlled smart home automation including smart plug, hub, voice assistant, and leak detector', '-Subway tile kitchen backsplash', '-Reserved covered parking and private garage                                                                                         Featured amenity', '-Terrace featuring barbecue pavilion and fire pits                                                                                         Featured amenity', '-Private patio or Juliet balcony', '-Easy access to I-5 Freeway', '-Elevator access', '-Kitchen island or breakfast bar with pendent lighting available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Prices Change Daily', 'Flexible Lease Terms']
